of Agriculture spokeswoman. ''He had dumped the load and was going back to get
more water when he crashed,'' Compton said. The cause of the crash is under
investigation. The pilot, George A. Burton, 48, had been fighting a fire that
reportedly threatened about a dozen homes near Fort Myers.
</P>
